Text:
This show is still on?  Color me surprised.  I guess NBC is being kind and airing the whole season.  If it actually gets picked up for a second one, I'll be DOUBLY SURPRISED!  Like this: O_O

Seriously, though, shows with laugh tracks are soooo 90's.  Don't tell me when I'm supposed to laugh, ho!  If it's funny, I'll laugh!
